short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Integrates with Quickli to provide advanced in-browser functionality such as form competion.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Quickli Chrome Extension is a tool for mortgage brokers. It allows you to perform advanced tasks such as uploading your Quickli scenarios into online lender serviceability calculators in order to help you to quickly finalize deals.
